title: The Samsung Galaxy Book Vol. 3
description:
The ultimate guide to the latest Galaxy apps so that you can get more from your device. Follow our in-depth guides to the wide range of built-in and downloadable apps available for your Samsung Galaxy device, from Settings and the Samsung Hub to Story Album and S Translator. Discover the potential of your Galaxy device to make your life much simpler and more fun! 

Every Samsung Galaxy question answered 
- Discover how to get started with your device, use it to keep in touch, on the move, to organize your life, manage your work and entertain. 

Be entertained
- Download the hottest apps and media from Google Play and Samsung Apps and use Media players and Samsung Hubs to watch, play, listen and read. 

Get organised 
- Customise your device settings to meet your needs and use the S apps to organise your life. 

Store files 
- Never be without a file again with a range of file storage options on your device: Dropbox, Google Drive and Samsung Link.

Also inside...

- Every Samsung Galaxy question answered
- Customise settings - Make calls - Easy messaging - Explore the Google Play Store - Buy apps and media from Samsung Apps - Watch with Play Movies
- Listen with Play Music
- Read with Play Books
- Discover apps with S Suggest
- Use Samsung Hub
- Browse with Chrome - Browse with Internet app
- Send emails with the Email & Gmail apps
- Maseter S Note
- Use S Planner
- Navigate with Google Maps and Google Earth
- Watch YouTube videos
- Set up WatchON
- Discover new Camera shooting modes
- Organise images in Gallery
- Create fun pics with Paper Artist
- Create a Story Album
- Set up Facebook
- Set up Google+
- Start a video call with Hangouts
- Make video calls on Skype
- Chat with friends on ChatON
- Upload files to Dropbox
- Learn a language with S Translator
- Set up Find My Mobile
- Manage connections with Samsung Kies

The Samsung Galaxy Book Vol. 3
